msgstr ""

msgid "Modifies the overall lightness of the effect layer. Increase above 1.0 for a brighter, illuminated look (ideal for light themes), decrease below 1.0 for darker, moodier tones. Applied as part of backdrop-filter — effective only on compositors that support it."
